data.description: ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 3.75% (lender conditions have to be met)… MUST CHECK OUT this gorgeous 4 bedroom, 2 bath 2 car garage home with NO HOA!! Home includes a formal Living Room AND a family room with gas fireplace. The kitchen features granite countertops, a large pantry, stainless steel appliances, nice wood cabinets and a beautiful decorative tile backsplash. The large master suite has a walk-in closet and solid wood floors. The three additional bedrooms are large in size with one of the additional bedrooms featuring a private, in room vanity with a fully functional sink.  The spacious backyard includes a chlorinated inground swimming pool with a hot tub, fire pit, and is fully fenced in with wood privacy fence...Perfect for friendly gatherings and entertaining! **Sellers are motivated and are offering $5,000 in concessions for any necessary pool repairs.
